eu.kartoffelquadrat.xoxinternals.model

Class XoxInitSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.kartoffelquadrat.xoxinternals.model.XoxInitSettings

  • public class XoxInitSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    Bean that compiles all information required to initialize a new Xox game instance. Pass an instance of this class to the controller to create a new game session.
    Author:
    Maximilian Schiedermeier

      • XoxInitSettings

        public XoxInitSettings(java.util.LinkedList<Player> players,
                       java.lang.String creator)
        Overloaded constructor to directly set the players and indicate which player is the creator.
        Parameters:
        players - as the list of players participating in the game
        creator - as the name of the game creator (commonly the player who begins the game). Must match the string of exactly one of the player object name fields.
